aemon streams container output in real-time\n\n7. **`/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-pages-design.md`**\n   - Project pages UI design; doesn't directly reference logs/streaming implementation\n\n### Project Documentation\n\n8. **`/workspace/PROJECT.md`** (Lines 25-28)\n   - References need to capture all output from prompts and scripts\n   - Mentions need for log of LLM thoughts and script output\n   - Part of \"Log Contents\" feature requirements\n\n9. **`/workspace/CLAUDE.md`**\n   - Architecture overview mentioning `logs` command (line 19)\n   - Brief reference with no implementation details\n\n### Architecture Observations\n\nThese files collectively document:\n- **CLI interface:** `cloche logs <run-id> [--step <name>] [--type <full|script|llm>] [--follow]`\n- **Streaming mechanism:** Server-Sent Events (SSE) for real-time log tailing with `--follow` flag\n- **Log structure:** Unified full.log with per-step filterable logs (llm-*.log, script output)\n- **Implementation location:** gRPC bidirectional streaming between CLI and daemon, with SSE bridging to web clients"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ab208e02ca773d2f3 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 43436\ntool_uses: 16\nduration_ms: 25694</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7e3762fb-e565-4c0e-b9b1-9371ff7bfffd","uuid":"06ca3050-12b0-46a1-ac3b-e6df2d2934ec","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find all documentation files in /workspace that might reference log streaming, the `logs` command, `--follow` flag, broadcaster, SSE, or live output. Look in docs/, USAGE.md, README.md, and any .md files. I need the file paths and a brief summary of what they contain related to logging/streaming. Be thorough - check for *.md files throughout the repo.","agentId":"ab208e02ca773d2f3","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me create a comprehensive summary of all the documentation files that reference logging, streaming, and related